      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  THKJL0025 SELECT  ПЌАсДыЛѓРкШИЛчСжНФПЉКЮ
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3310-KJL0025-SELECT-RTN.

           INITIALIZE    TKJL0025-KEY
                         TRJL0025-REC

      *    БзЗьШИЛчФкЕх
           MOVE  WK-H-I-GROUP-CO-CD
             TO  KJL0025-PK-GROUP-CO-CD

